[00:34:45.000 --> 00:34:48.000]  God will direct our heart
[00:34:48.000 --> 00:34:54.000]  Now place your hands on your eyes
[00:34:54.000 --> 00:34:57.000]  and your ears
[00:34:57.000 --> 00:35:00.000]  Ask God to defend your eyes
[00:35:00.000 --> 00:35:02.000]  Protect your ears and your eyes
[00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:05.000]  From what you see and what you hear
[00:35:05.000 --> 00:35:07.000]  Pray for that
[00:35:07.000 --> 00:35:09.000]  Let's all stand
[00:35:09.000 --> 00:35:11.000]  And we'll finish with this prayer
[00:35:11.000 --> 00:35:13.000]  Father
[00:35:13.000 --> 00:35:15.000]  We thank you
[00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:17.000]  That you sent the Holy Spirit
[00:35:17.000 --> 00:35:19.000]  To guide us
[00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:20.000]  To help us
[00:35:20.000 --> 00:35:27.000]  Help us to depend on the Holy Spirit everyday
[00:35:27.000 --> 00:35:31.000]  This world is wicked and evil
[00:35:31.000 --> 00:35:34.000]  But you are greater
[00:35:34.000 --> 00:35:38.000]  You have conquered all on the cross
[00:35:38.000 --> 00:35:40.000]  May you help us to guard our heart
[00:35:40.000 --> 00:35:42.000]  Guard our innocence
[00:35:42.000 --> 00:35:44.000]  Guard our purity
[00:35:44.000 --> 00:35:46.000]  For Jesus Christ
[00:35:46.000 --> 00:35:49.000]  And the church said, Amen
